(440, '2011-09-20', 'Team Fortress 2 Update Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_6319\" style=\"display: ;\">
<p>Updates to Team Fortress 2 have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The major changes include:<br/><br/><b>Team Fortress 2</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Updated the Pilotka so it can be crafted, traded, and gift-wrapped<br/><li>Updated the Stahlhelm so it can be crafted, traded, and gift-wrapped<br/><li>Updated the physics for the Sticky Jumper projectiles so they behave like regular sticky bombs<br/></li></li></li></ul></p>
