(440, '2011-11-29', 'Team Fortress 2, Day of Defeat: Source and Half-Life 2: Deathmatch Updates Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_6887\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Updates to Team Fortress 2, Day of Defeat: Source and Half-Life 2: Deathmatch have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The major changes include:<br/><br/><b>Source Engine Changes (TF2, DoD:S, HL2:DM)</b><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Dramatically improved the dynamic model loading system\'s memory usage, performance, and stability<br/><li>Reduced memory usage on systems running Windows XP, Windows Vista, and Windows 7<br/><li>Improved alt-tab handling under Windows Vista and Windows 7<br/></li></li></li></ul></p>
